title: The Steve Harvey Show Season 1 (fixed files)
description:
The torrent for The Steve Harvey Show - Season 1 has 3 corrupted files and 1 truncated file.

The corrupted files have been fixed and are in this torrent:
The Steve Harvey Show 1x13 - Coming To Chicago.mp4
The Steve Harvey Show 1x20 - Love With Interest.mp4
The Steve Harvey Show 1x21 - Can't Buy Me Love.mp4

The truncated file is "The Steve Harvey Show 1x18 Guess Who's Not Coming to Dinner.avi" and I do NOT have the fix for this. Maybe somebody else would be kind enough to upload it?

P.S. Dear God, would somebody please seed the rest of the seasons?!
